yarangi.graphics.quadraturin.thread
Class LoopyChainedThread

java.lang.Object
  yarangi.graphics.quadraturin.thread.ChainedThreadSkeleton
      yarangi.graphics.quadraturin.thread.LoopyChainedThread
All Implemented Interfaces:
Runnable, IChainedThread
public class LoopyChainedThread
extends ChainedThreadSkeleton
implements Runnable

Represent a thread in a sequential thread execution scheme.Each of the sequence Chainable-s runs a loop, with:

  • #runPreUnLock
  • #runBody()
  • #runPostLock()

    stages in each iteration. The #runBody() is only executed, when previous thread in the sequence have finished it's own body. ChainedThreadSkeleton.getOrdial() number is the turn of this Chainable in the order of execution.

    Author:
    Dve Yarangi
